{
  "text": "Actually, in [CITATION_1] terms are defined as a subclass of pseudo-terms satisfying some syntactical conditions. We could do the same here but as we will only consider typed terms this is not necessary (all well-typed pseudo-terms are terms).",
  "citation_candidates": [
